Description: Essential oils and resinoids; perfumery, cosmetic or toilet preparations

Subentries.Description: Mixtures of odoriferous substances and mixtures (including alcoholic solutions) with a basis of one or more of these substances, of a kind used as raw materials in industry; other preparations based on odoriferous substances, of a kind used for the manufacture of beverages:
Containing no alcohol or not over 10 percent of alcohol by weight
Perfume oil mixtures and blends, consisting of products ready for use as finished perfume bases
Containing over 10 percent of alcohol by weight
Perfume oil mixtures and blends, consisting of products ready for use as finished perfume bases
